* "HOWTO 0.1.1":/cozybit/open80211s/wiki/wiki:HOWTO-0.1.1

h2. Features
* Unicast forwarding using fixed path tables, with mesh ttl decrementing.
* Path table modifiable from user space (add new paths, show table, delete all paths).
* Mesh statistics via /proc/net/mesh.
* zd1211-rw device support.
* Mesh beaconing support.
* Mesh ID modifiable from userspace.

h2. Known issues
* Broadcast forwarding is not implemented.
